Dorian Lough https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorian_Lough 0 Dorian Tristan Lough (born 27 April 1966 in Kensington, London) is an English actor who appeared as DS Dave Satchell in Trial Retribution. He has also played Ray Taylor in EastEnders. Lough is also known for starring in the music video for the Radiohead song "Just".
